dlentry.dd:
For example, the following usage in the Directory Template property generates a new
          directory every
          minute:/outputfiles/${YY()}-${MM()}-${DD()}-${hh()}-${every(1,mm())}

To include seconds in the directories and generate a new directory every 60 seconds,
          replace the seconds datetime variable as
          follows:/outputfiles/${YY()}-${MM()}-${DD()}-${hh()}-${mm()}-${every(60,ss())}

For example, since 65% of the Java heap size is the recommended maximum, the following
          expression is the default memory limit for a pipeline:
          ${jvm:maxMemoryMB() * 0.65}
